  <brief_title>Central Blood Volume in Hypotensive Dialysis Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Registration of Central Blood Volume in Hypotensive Dialysis Patients - a Comparison of Thoracic Impedance and Central Venous Saturation Monitoring</official_title>
  <sponsors>
